Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:13.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,カラダはこんなにクタクタに疲れてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:24.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ココロはどうしてドキドキが止まらないんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日とちがう明日があること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:38.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,信じられる自分がいるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:40.83,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,今日も走れ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:47.09,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,倒れたって恥ずかしくない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:51.33,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,もう一度立ち上がれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:57.71,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,あと少しでたどり着けそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:01.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,予感がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,夢の地図なんていらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:12.73,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,目指す場所はもうずっと決まっている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:21.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,新しい世界にいま出会いたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:13.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,明明身體這麼疲憊不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:24.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼卻抑制不住內心的激動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,和昨天不同 明天是新的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:38.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果相信自己的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:40.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也邁開大步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:47.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被打倒也不覺得丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:51.33,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,再次站起來就行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:57.71,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點就能抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:01.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我有這種預感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不需要什麼夢幻地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:12.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目標早已決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:21.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,好想立刻邂逅全新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:03.24,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ボクの見ていた　一人分の景色の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:09.24,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君の色があたりまえになる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:13.46,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,知らなかった心地いい距離や
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:17.18,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,くだらない意地の張り合い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:21.89,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほらまたすぐに笑い合えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:28.92,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,日常を重ね合って行く　途切れず強くなって行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:37.11,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ボクの心はきっと君の半分が満たすんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:38.74,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぴったりと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:43.20,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと寄り添って生きて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:46.79,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ボク等なんだか似てるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:53.37,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,頼りないとこも 補ってちょうどいいとこも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:57.57,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちゃんと向き合って生きて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:00.59,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然の引力は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:10.20,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,神様だって予測できない必然示してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:03.24,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我所看到的 一人份的景色中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:09.24,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的顏色 漸漸變得司空見慣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:13.46,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,進入從未體驗過的愜意距離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:17.18,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊的賭氣之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:21.89,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,看 馬上又笑在一塊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:28.92,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的日常漸漸重合 不斷變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:37.11,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,有你作「半」一定能填補我心中的空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:38.74,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如此的契合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:43.20,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,再更靠近一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:46.79,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們好像很相似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:53.37,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不可靠的地方也都能互相彌補
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:57.57,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,好好面對彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:00.59,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然的引力諭示著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:10.20,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,連神明都無法預測的必然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是地下城對我們的憎惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它把藏身於此的我們視為眼中釘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烏拉諾斯 你的祈禱哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒聽說會發生這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是階層主麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:27.90,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1100,164)}{\fad(450,450)}眷族的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:27.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1100,104)}{\fad(450,450)}Familiar Myth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕緊去救他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的打算用這只隊伍去救他們麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去救他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個不合格的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你並沒有做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草小姐 上神大人就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 千萬不要勉強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒戲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咆..咆哮？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變這樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你會妨礙到貝爾大人 所以把你拖走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好感謝我們家那位來者不拒的老好人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把能找到的武器和冒險者全都找來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要討伐階層主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了 安朵美達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是一般的階層主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退路已經被切斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事實上 我們已不可能離開這個階層了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非打倒那個傢伙 不然就無法逃離這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小的們 準備和那個怪物大幹一場吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把鎮上的傢伙全都給我趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些畏縮怕事滅自家威風的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將永遠不准再踏入這個鎮子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家看看咱們冒險者的骨氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快離開那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無形鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和通常的階層主不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛在能力到達了等級5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利昂 援軍到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在起 鎮上的魔導師們將開始進行詠唱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你繼續吸引歌利亞的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起分散敵人的注意力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒 小的們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安朵美達將親自擔當誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就放心大膽地開始詠唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給它來一發大的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯斯 這筆帳我記下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爭取時間 只要撐到詠唱結束..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然厲害..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器多得是 壞了就趕緊換一把
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是臨時拼湊的隊伍 就別管什麼配合了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不彼此妨礙就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按各自的性子去戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 前鋒後撤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要送它一份大禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我狠狠地打！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣幹掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我再生..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請克朗尼先生擋住周圍的怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我們去壓制歌利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓它繼續肆虐下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要爭取到時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚有戰力的魔導師就能施放出下一輪魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這樣還不管用 就一輪接一輪..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到打倒它為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫斯緹雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支援者小姐 你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請把能找到的裝備都搜集過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了吧 拜託你回鎮上一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草大人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到剛才的爆炸她就跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是去櫻花他們那邊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利昂 你這樣會死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也必須做我該做的才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙太硬了 想攻擊魔石也無從下手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去遲早..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便這樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要還有希望..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草 拿盾來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 會死的..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花會死的..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你 千草
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想成為只會嘴上說說的卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想成為眼看他人犧牲而無動於衷的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利昂 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰閃電
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花大人 櫻花大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生 請回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾 他的情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有呼吸..不過傷口很深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利昂 這裏交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草小姐 之後就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去吧 精靈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡可能多爭取一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾絕對會醒過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會醒過來 打倒那個怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女神赫斯緹雅..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也見識過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾的話一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾的話一定能打倒那個怪獸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾 醒一醒啊貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在戰鬥 面對那麼可怕的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拯救大家的只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來 貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾 貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上神大人 我明白的 我聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 身體卻怎麼都..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體怎麼都動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動啊 動啊 快動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須去戰鬥 為了上神大人為了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有資格被稱為英雄的..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既不是仗劍之人 也不是舉盾之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不是療傷止痛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能賭上自己性命的人 才能被稱為英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保護同伴拯救紅顏  賭上自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭遇挫折也沒關係 備受打擊也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情哭泣吧 勝者永遠存在於敗者之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貫徹你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊出你的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是最帥氣的男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不愧對那個人..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更為了拯救重要的同伴們..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾大人..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你 貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃燒憧憬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊出願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界限解除？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓它們過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻幽遠森林的上空..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限繁星點綴無窮夜天..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回應我愚鈍的請求..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再度賜下星火之加護..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以光之慈悲寬恕棄汝而去之人..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種高速戰鬥中同時進行詠唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然這麼高..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨口拙舌 誠惶誠恐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰無不勝的吾之武神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無上尊天的指引啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請賦予卑小之身以巍然御體之神力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我這麼說很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我真的需要幫助一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 讓我粉碎你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流離之冽風..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流浪之旅人..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橫跨蒼穹穿越荒野..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我也得拿出看家本領了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攜星屑之芒以禦敵..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光明之風
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.53,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Luminos Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自天降臨 一統大地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神武鬥征 布都御魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力的結界..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頂不住了..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火月！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 克羅佐的魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然超越了原型？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要把執念和同伴放在天平上比較
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那只是執念而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對不講理的壓倒性力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅憑一股微不足道的力量實現逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄的一擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連那一擊也..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的貝爾·克朗尼..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能夠更快..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更強..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更高地飛躍！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾大人 貝爾大人成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:20:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一手嘛 小小新秀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我荷米斯確實見識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無資質？別說傻話了 宙斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的孫子 你的臨別贈禮是貨真價實的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的眷族留下的最後的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉動了 時代要向前轉動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會親眼見證
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將發生在這裏 這塊歐拉麗大地的..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,載入史冊的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄們的興衰榮辱 他們的生與死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親愛的他們所編織的 眷族的故事..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Familiar Myth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角度很刁鑽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以發生了那種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在喝著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很努力呢
